OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly dry day
OL,6,Fwith some bright intervals. A few
OL,7,Flight showers are possible, especially
OL,8,Ftowards the evening. Feeling rather
OL,9,Fcool despite the light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA largely dry start to the
OL,12,Fevening with some brightness. Becoming
OL,13,Fcloudy with frequent showers arriving,
OL,14,Fturning wintry later over Shetland.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,17,Fduring the morning, turning to snow on
OL,18,Fthe hills. A drier afternoon with
OL,19,Fsunny spells. Feeling cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
